[SPEAKER_02]: They did not approve my contract.

62
00:03:32,681 --> 00:03:42,248
[SPEAKER_02]: The board then voted that since it wasn't a bonus, it was actually my salary to rescind the vote for it to be a bonus because they wouldn't approve the contract.

